{"tid":1301831,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[Brainstorm 吓] 林奠壽終正寢百萬人超渡會","createTime":"2019-07-09T17:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T20:34:04.000Z","uid":266977,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0f48b00327f990d96c96f6b2bff8d8ce27d79b98","tid":1301831,"uid":266977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:44:58.000Z","msg":"<strong>背景</strong><br />\n一區之長既然形容自已 &rdquo;完全失敗&rdquo; &rdquo;壽終正寢&rdquo;，就算虛情假意聲稱要服務市民， 其實都只係成為戀棧塵世，為禍人間嘅冤魂中陰身。成為中共同世界負累。<br />\n<br />\n為咗幫佢戒除貪嗔癡早登極樂，香港人應該搞場<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">百萬人超渡會送佢上路</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>作用</strong><br />\n香港近日係全球焦點, 如果響世界傳媒面前同林鄭搞場百萬人葬禮, 對佢同土共係極大羞辱。<br />\n<br />\n中共仲係咪忍到手保佢? 以後佢仲點外訪? 係咪有機會加快佢落台?<br />\n<br />\n難得林鄭一句壽終正寢有位畀人入, 大家一齊Brainstorm吓!<br />\n<br />\n<strong>內容</strong><br />\n1.  Set 個靈堂响中環 / 禮賓府附近<br />\n2.  集氣遊行, 去到靈堂前全日一組組人三鞠躬。相信畫面幾震撼。<br />\n3. 含蓄嘅可以去靜靜哋默衰<br />\n4. 好sad嘅禮成之後可以四圍哭墳飲解穢酒，適隨尊便<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>口號</strong><br />\n林奠己死 普選當立 <br />\n+ 繼續5 大訴求"},{"pid":"35dfc80c4b70a22cd163ebd179f74d825ae0d236","tid":1301831,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:47:24.000Z","msg":"個人意見 冇乜用 似純發洩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>7.10</strong> - <ins>TVB港姐</ins> - <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1300556\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/1300556</a><br />\n<strong>7.10</strong> - <ins>麥小姐追思會</ins> ＠ 中環愛丁堡廣場 - 19:00~22:30<br />\n<strong>7.11</strong> - <ins>梁烈士公眾告別禮</ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung